---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHero from '@/components/content/SectionHero.vue';
import SectionTwoColumn from '@/components/content/SectionTwoColumn.vue';
import Job from '@/components/content/Job.vue';
---

<Layout title='Progress Ireland'>
  <SectionHero title='Helping Ireland reach its potential.' />
  <SectionTwoColumn
    id='our-mission'
    title='Mission'
  >
    <div slot='leftColumn'>
      <h3
        class='font-headings text-pi-heading-4 lg:text-pi-heading-3 text-charcoal-bright lg:max-w-[620px]'
      >
        Building Irish capacity for the next stage of growth.
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div slot='rightColumn'>
      <div class='w-full'>
        <p
          class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          Ireland has come a long way. But progress won is easily lost, and this
          upward trend is threatened by housing shortages, inadequate
          infrastructure, and an over-dependence on multinationals. To solve
          these problems we need to improve the supply of policy ideas in
          Ireland.
        </p>

        <p
          class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          Progress Ireland is a new independent think tank dedicated to
          advancing economic and scientific progress in Ireland.
        </p>

        <div
          class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:gap-x-pi-20 mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          <div class='w-full lg:w-1/3'>
            <h4 class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright'>
              We are non-partisan.
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class='w-full lg:w-2/3'>
            <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
              We are independent of any lobby or donor. We are supported by a
              wide range of private individuals who share our mission.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:gap-x-pi-20 mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          <div class='w-full lg:w-1/3'>
            <h4 class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright'>
              We believe in policy.
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class='w-full lg:w-2/3'>
            <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
              We sincerely believe that evidence-based and creative policymaking
              can solve Ireland's most pressing problems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:gap-x-pi-20 mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          <div class='w-full lg:w-1/3'>
            <h4 class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright'>
              We believe in win-win politics.
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class='w-full lg:w-2/3'>
            <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
              The policies that are most likely to be implemented, and the ones
              that work, distribute their benefits widely.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:gap-x-pi-20 mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          <div class='w-full lg:w-1/3'>
            <h4 class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright'>
              We believe in building.
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class='w-full lg:w-2/3'>
            <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
              Building is the solution to many of Ireland's most pressing
              problems, from expensive housing to political polarisation,
              climate change and quality of life.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:gap-x-pi-20 mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          <div class='w-full lg:w-1/3'>
            <h4 class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright'>
              We believe in the market.
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class='w-full lg:w-2/3'>
            <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
              To build the best version of Ireland we will need to draw on the
              resources and talents of all parts of society, from Ireland and
              overseas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:gap-x-pi-20 mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pi-20'
        >
          <div class='w-full lg:w-1/3'>
            <h4 class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright'>
              We believe in the state.
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class='w-full lg:w-2/3'>
            <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
              To build the best version of Ireland we will need a renewed state
              with more ambition and more capabilities than it has today.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class='text-pi-body-3-light text-charcoal-bright'>
          Progress Ireland will launch this Autumn. In the interim if you have
          an idea, a question, or would like to apply for one of our open roles,
          get in touch at <a
            href='mailto:hello@progressireland.org'
            class='underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-charcoal-light transition'
            >hello@progressireland.org</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionTwoColumn>

  <SectionTwoColumn
    id='team'
    title='Team'
  >
    <div slot='rightColumn'>
      <Job
        client:load
        title='Seán Keyes (Executive Director)'
      />
      <Job
        client:load
        title="Seán O'Neill McPartlin (Director of Housing Policy)"
      />
      <Job
        client:load
        title='Luke Fehily (Director of Science and Innovation Policy)'
      />
      <Job
        client:load
        title='Fergus McCullough (Director of Operations)'
      />
    </div>
  </SectionTwoColumn>

  <SectionTwoColumn
    id='governance'
    title='Governance'
  >
    <div slot='rightColumn'>
      <Job
        client:load
        title='Fiona Cormican (Non-executive Director)'
      />
      <Job
        client:load
        title='Donal de Buitleir (Non-executive Director)'
      />
    </div>
  </SectionTwoColumn>

  <SectionTwoColumn
    id='opportunities'
    title='Opportunities'
  >
    <div slot='leftColumn'>
      <h3
        class='font-headings text-pi-heading-4 lg:text-pi-heading-3 text-charcoal-bright lg:max-w-[572px] mb-pi-15 lg:mb-pb-10'
      >
        We're always on the lookout for talented policy experts to join our
        team.
      </h3>
      <p class='text-pi-body-3-bold text-charcoal-bright lg:max-w-[572px]'>
        Click on the open roles or reach us at <a
          href='mailto:jobs@progressireland.org'>jobs@progressireland.org.</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
    <div slot='rightColumn'>
      <Job
        title='Senior Economist'
        attributes={['Dublin', 'Hybrid', 'Full Time']}
        link='https://fossil-sidecar-40a.notion.site/Senior-Economist-98de6cab91084be09e4c703c772f60eb'
      />
      <Job
        title='Design your own role'
        attributes={['Dublin', 'Hybrid', 'Full Time']}
        link='https://fossil-sidecar-40a.notion.site/Design-your-own-role-729b6b2c6af34da3833ef0d900439ae9'
      />
    </div>
  </SectionTwoColumn>
</Layout>
